st words we are to use in ap-</div><div class="t mf53 x1c he y440 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">proaching God He places the assurance of </div><div class="t m128 x1c he y477 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our divine relationship, &apos;Our Father.&apos; </div><div class="t m1e7 x17a h21 y477 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;—</div><div class="t m882 x1c h21 y305 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Thoughts From the Mount of Blessing, </div><div class="t m107d x1c he ya63 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1956 ed., p. 103. </div><div class="t m7cb x56 he y425 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t mfc5 x9f he y425 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did Christ become the Su-</div><div class="t mb7a x1c he y324 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preme Example for stewards? John </div><div class="t m19b x1c he y5f0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3:16; Titus 2:14, first part. </div><div class="t m1be x4b h1 y1e5 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Man, Steward of God&apos;s Gifts </div><div class="t m1bd x7 he y189 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m7c7 x9f he yc9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When and how was the practice </div><div class="t m1799 x1c he y885 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of stewardship introduced to man? </div><div class="t mf5e x1c he y384 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen. 2:15; 1 Cor. 4:1, 7. </div><div class="t m3dac x52 h36 y44 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[5] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
